<section class="border-b border-[#dce5da] bg-white/55 py-16">
    <div class="section-shell grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
        <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-normal text-[#0f766e]">Problem</p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-normal text-[#13201d] md:text-4xl">
                Private files should not live forever in chat history
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-[#52625d]">
                People usually send private files straight through Telegram, Slack, Discord, or email because it is fast. The problem is that the file can stay in chat history, attachments, backups, and forwarded threads much longer than you wanted.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-[#52625d]">
                Instead of sending the original file, share a temporary encrypted SecShare link.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Config files</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Pass environment-specific config without leaving the raw file in chat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Logs</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Send logs for debugging and let the link expire after the handoff.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Database dumps</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Move a dump to someone who needs it without attaching it directly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Credentials and secrets</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Share a secret once, with a short expiration and download limit.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Private documents</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Send PDFs, archives, and other private files as temporary links.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#dce5da] bg-[#fbfcf8] p-5">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#13201d]">Team handoff</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[#52625d]">Move one file between teammates, machines, or clients and be done.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
